---
description: "High-risk areas policy"
alwaysApply: true
---

High-risk change policy (fail closed):
- auth/permissions/crypto/payments: must be flagged in artifacts/current/risk.md
- deps changes: require artifacts/current/dependency-review.md
- docker/ci changes: require artifacts/current/infra-review.md
- db migrations: require artifacts/current/db-review.md with reversibility and rollback notes

If uncertain about risk impact, mark the task BLOCKED and explain precisely what info is missing.
